title: JAKQ Blitzkrieg Squad - Super Sentai
description:
This is a reseed of the second generation Super Sentai show from 1977. As each generation is based on a theme, this team adopted playing cards; Jack, Ace, King and Queen.

Of particular note is the Queen ranger, an empowered woman who kicked ass. That was pretty rare, if nonexistent, in any 70s show. Another great aspect was the music, which is also collected here.

The first three episodes are English subbed by Love & Careand I think all the unsubbed DVD raws come courtesy of BunnyhatJAKQ vs Goranger is from GUIS (http://www.grownupsinspandex.com/).

JAKQ soundtracks are from Citsrusâ€™ Tokusatsu Super Music Collection.
